high_descs: Pick up the glass from the sink.
Bring the glass to the microwave.
Heat the glass in the microwave.
Bring the glass to the wooden rack.
Put the glass on the wooden rack.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated glass on the wooden rack.

high_descs: move forward towards the shelf and then right towards the sink
pick up the glass cup from the sink
turn around and head towards the gas cooker
place the glass cup in the microwave oven above the gas cooker, allow to heat up and then take it out
turn left and move towards the shelf
place the glass cup on the shelf

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the sink.
Pick up the glass cup from the sink.
Turn around, walk towards the stove on your right, look up above the stove to find a microwave.
Open the microwave, place the cup in it, heat it up, and take the cup out of microwave.
Turn left, head towards the wall, and then turn right towards the wooden shelf.
Place the cup to the right of the green sponge on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm glass cup on the wooden shelf.
